prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon-style watercolor illustration of a slightly frazzled, but happy, squirrel wearing a tiny party hat, struggling to balance a giant, teetering stack of birthday presents that are much larger than it is. The squirrel has a determined and comical expression on its face. The gifts are wrapped in colorful, mismatched paper. In the center, elegantly integrated amongst the presents, the words "happy birthday" are written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script. The entire scene is a flat 2D artwork in a watercolor painting style, featuring soft flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, a subtle paper texture, and organic paint bleeds around the edges of the squirrel and presents. The background is a simple, light wash of color.
